### Frontend Component

We will update the intake UI to support Excel parsing, vendor selection, and automated form filling.

#### [MODIFY] [IntakeForm.tsx](file:///c:/Users/intern.digitaltransf/Desktop/Project_1/vendorlens-frontend/src/components/IntakeForm.tsx)
- Integrate a new file upload handler:
  - When an Excel file is uploaded, send it to `http://localhost:8000/vendor/parse-excel`.
  - Receive the list of parsed vendors.
  - Render an interactive **dropdown menu** listing the names and ID/BP numbers of the parsed vendors: `Name (BP Number)`.
  - Selecting a vendor from the dropdown automatically populates the form inputs (Legal Name, Domain, registration/tax numbers, address, PAN, MSME, etc.) in the manual form section.
  - The user can review, edit, or fill any missing values.
  - Submitting the form calls `POST http://localhost:8000/vendor/intake` with the selected/populated vendor details.

